        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1945-01-09T03:00:00-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1945-01-09T03:00:00-05:00" n="7" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d7">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">390.1115A/1–945: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The Ambassador in China</hi> (<persName type="from">
                        <hi rend="italic">Hurley</hi>
                    </persName>) <hi rend="italic">to the <gloss type="to">Secretary of
                            State</gloss>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Chungking</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1945-01-09T15:00:00+07:00">January 9, 1945—3 p.m.</date>
                        <lb/> [Received 3:07 p.m.]</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>25. Embassy’s telegram 81 to Delhi<note n="32" xml:id="d7fn32">Telegram No. 81,
                        December 23, 1944, 3 p.m., to the Commissioner at New Delhi (Merrell), not
                        printed.</note> referred to Government personnel only (Department’s 34,
                    January 6<note n="33" xml:id="d7fn33">Not printed.</note>). Embassy is
                    continuing endeavors to facilitate withdrawal from China of non-essential
                    Americans (Embassy’s 3, January 2). This program has been retarded due to
                    temporary stabilization of military situation and it is feared would be
                    completely nullified were additional civilians other than Government personnel
                    authorized to proceed to China except in cases of special emergency.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Hurley</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
